localString.value: A large powerful contruct, presumeably guarding something of great secrecy and importance...
This piecemeal of cloth was crafted by a skilled tailor.
Pick it up, you know you want to...

Sorry for the dissapointment, surely you don't think I'd really let you steal something of value? Regardless, aquiring this means you are at least a skillful rogue, return it to me and I may have work for you. - Jaden Tyln
The Kunai is a small dagger type tool which serves primarily as a ultilty knife for the Kunai guild. It can be used as a versitle weapon or to disable traps and pick locks among other things.
Hearty billows fan the forge-borne flames. The air is blisteringly hot, leaving you feel light-headed and not quite yourself.
This sturdy blacksmith's anvil bears the dented sheen of long use. Something in you wonders what great weapons and armor have been shaped upon its well-worn surface.
This is a fletchers desk used for making arrows.

The grease covered contraption before you contains the necessary tools, clamps, cutter, vials and other assorted bits needed to use the tinkering skill. A tinkerer tool is needed to activate and use parts of the set.
The wicker bulls-eye of this archery target bears a fresh coat of paint.
Restricted Area - Tresspassers will be executed on sight
Beyond this door lies the Vault, we will not accept any resonsilbility for injury or death that results from an attempt to steal our valuables, you have been warned. - the Tylns
